br />\n<br />\n我明白要過自己心理關口係好難，要晒好多時間，但要做到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">突破中共封鎖</span>既文宣，就只能夠咁。"},{"pid":"6721a1b54740bef550843a369a2187f1675aa9c5","tid":1717352,"uid":332503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ebbc0077f6e48e32bdfa6eb93d9153ca40f165b","tid":1717352,"uid":74532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"721cfdafff4e0b44160e36e74f9e10157b1c5004","tid":1717352,"uid":332503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e771e690efefa246702cc98454c1c6c07d29597","tid":1717352,"uid":74532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:36:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Don&rsquo;t be silly<br />\n想我地死嘅支那人先係majority<br />\n支那人無一個係無辜<br />\n勿洗白<br />\n<br />\n仲有！無nds, 無大陸, 無中國<br />\n<br />\n得支那！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再叫香港人！反抗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T22:27:35.000Z","msg":"成日話藍屍nds冇腦盲反<br />\n自己卻又盲反人地<br />\n<br />\n風向撚明白晒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你咪同藍絲支那人講道理囉<br />\n150個都有好人架<br />\n藍絲都有身不由己架<br />\n警察都有白警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你就真係無腦<br />\n唔意同就叫人風向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:58:34.000Z","msg":"話你係風向撚咩，你又唔夠專業<br />\n詭辯技巧又未學夠<br />\n<br />\n首先，同你講NDS姐係內地生<br />\n你就spin去150人藍屍白警<br />\n轉移視線都唔係咁勉強嘅下話？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二，要避免人地標籤你，最好既辦法系自己戴上呢個標籤<br />\n你實際上就係一條風向撚<br />\n所以先下手為強話我屈你係風向撚<br />\n好可惜呢d技巧太基礎用得太唔sophisticated<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三，<br />\n你刻意分化覺醒嘅NDS手足<br />\n深化我地之間嘅矛盾<br />\n就係希望閹割我哋獲得更多手足既來源<br />\n你既目的好明顯喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你係真&middot;手足，麻煩你用logic說服我<br />\n唔好話我屈你係風向撚之後唔比機會你解釋"},{"pid":"aeae2d03f1cc1796d559556504058749278505c5","tid":1717352,"uid":304306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:59:30.000Z","msg":"NDS唔係Non Domestic  Student咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d750434fd8f6bc3563a63b372808cda456ee6b","tid":1717352,"uid":332503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeae2d03f1cc1796d559556504058749278505c5","tid":1717352,"uid":304306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:59:30.000Z","msg":"NDS唔係Non Domestic  Student咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:00:22.000Z","msg":"呢到系特指內地生"}]}